{"type": "article", "id": 62246, "title": "这个复古电子管时钟，用手机就能控制｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-20T22:05:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 49383, "name": "Grohe"}, {"id": 17504, "name": "A.P.C."}, {"id": 57397, "name": "Millclock Company"}, {"id": 57398, "name": "Masaaki Hiromura"}, {"id": 57399, "name": "Seokmoon Woo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 115, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190320215134TEDHzf9u28FykBnq.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #6c6c6c; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #6c6c6c} </style>  </p><h3>Swivel Projector by Seokmoon Woo</h3><p>设计师 Seokmoon Woo 创造了一款名为 Swivel Projector 的便携式投影仪，仅有手掌大小，可以放在口袋里。用户可以通过旋转内部零件来打开。当隐藏的镜头出现时，它就可以运行了。</p><p>当投影机不使用时，任何可识别的功能，如镜头和电源输入都隐藏在内部和外部，只有在旋转表圈时才会显露出来。这个操作不仅可以打开设备，还可以确保将其定位在正确的角度，以使图像正确显示在墙上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215203IPdqKZ0f76U5wCcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215204cgzGJvxpUBWAfN52.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215204Y39ITrVD1Gjpfiln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215204AnYIKC80Sv4JVbEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215204nrhPe0cCuypxSdWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215204CXvgHmzsSylN1i5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215204P6o03LvBbykO8ac9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/2019/03/20/a-truly-pocket-sized-projector/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>ZIN18 Reborn Clock by Millclock Company</h3><p>ZIN18 Reborn 时钟是一个复古的电子管时钟，每一颗灯泡都是手工制作，点亮时功率很低，但充满了蒸汽朋克美学，它由 Millclock 公司的设计师和工匠设计</p><p>ZIN 18 Reborn 时钟支持智能手机控制，还装配有触摸感应面板来让你调整时间。值得一提的是，如果没有出现重大损坏情况，它可以为你无故障工作至少 20 年。</p><p>ZIN18 Reborn 是一个六管钟，特点是 Millclock 公司的 ZIN18 数码管。这些管子完全是手工制作的，比半个世纪前的管子使用了更好的材料和制造工艺。它们的能量也非常低。目前，它在众筹网站 Kickstarter 的售价为 836 挪威克朗，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1989465642/zin18-the-new-nixie-tube-and-clocks\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215247Tgj80un6YfciJSzK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215247c6FUo4TXsCRpAQ27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903202152479WxEnbYpsZ8HtkUJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032021524819smgjaxib8kcuCT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215248grLTlaZDxQfUcuEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Round 16 by A.P.C. </h3><p>法国时尚品牌 A.P.C. 发布了这一季最新的床上用品系列 Round 16 ，包括多款被毯、枕头等单品，其中不少以诸如 Prelude in E （E 大调前奏曲）和 Fugue in C （C 大调赋格曲）等著名古典音乐作品命名，数款枕头也被取名为 Andante（行板）和 Crescendo （渐强）等音乐术语，充分体现了 A.P.C. 主理人 Jean Touitou 对于乐谱的热情。</p><p>Round 16 系列所有产品均由手工打造并且循环使用了此前余下的布料，也是品牌致力于时尚界可持续发展的表现。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215329RV7C8DJYEprZSXzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903202153280UliRDF2cwr3x6Y5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215329gcoehHnwOBsZAbip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903202153296xaQUZoXc0IGs2d8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215330Sr8qxOGavBt1UIj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215329of3dx6vBgiIyKSOQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215330sWzI8KV7A6201jyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215330Fpo8b3r9ZG1wLYeV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215330btVLHRjyO6mQz2J4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215330nuDxdaOVEov85CIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215331x0cCMLYiNKJ1rZwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215330WUer2iK0VPdw8pOk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Olympic Games pictograms by Masaaki Hiromura</h3><p>东京 2020 年夏季奥运会最近公布奥运会竞技项目图标。全套象形图标共有 50 个，涵盖 33 个不同的运动项目，包括空手道、滑板、冲浪等深受年轻人喜爱的竞技项目。</p><p>整套设计由日本平面设计大师 Hiromura Masaaki 操刀，项目历时近两年。灵感来源于 1964 年东京奥运会竞技图标，这是奥运会首次采用图标形式展示竞技项目。</p><p>“上辈留存的设计是一笔伟大的遗产”， Hiromura Masaaki 说道，“设计要与时代共进，所以我尝试融入运动员的活力，用青春的代表——肌肉，极简现代设计风格组成这套新图标。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\tp.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none}   <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t08510av1yb\" allowfullscreen=\"“true&quot;\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903202154592ALv3xOGhfVnl0c5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.010152\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215459mGvF90pyxHij3O2X.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.018190\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215459XgkF2GlE897SMsR3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215500l6SCFGoVbzty5s1D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215500X0lP1qgxHnrLO8SA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>The Atrio Icon 3D and Allure Brilliant Icon 3D taps by Grohe&nbsp;</h3><p>德国浴室和厨房制造商 Grohe 使用 3D 打印的方式重新构想了其两款畅销的水龙头款式，其原型是 Atrio 和 Allure Brilliant 系列产品。</p><p>新款水龙头是使用 3D 金属打印制作的，Atrio Icon 3D 模型采用薄而弯曲的喷口，中间有一个微妙的凹槽，而 Allure Brilliant Icon 3D 的形状更加棱角分明，中心完全中空。</p><p>Grohe 是欧洲第一家采用 3D 打印制造技术的领先卫浴公司，这种生产方法可以根据客户的意愿提供个性化的设计定制方式。</p><p>两种款式均采用拉丝钢表面处理，配有冷热手柄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215629y6LFqb53MPgZtGX8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215629JphwzyaiL9T28UxY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320215629h7nwBm9tIZAsUdpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.285533\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}